data.description:
Introducing an exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom Prattville residence in the serene Bent Tree neighborhood. This captivating home has been meticulously maintained, boasting a extraordinary list of  top-of-the-line upgrades such as new roof, new HVAC, new stove & pristine granite countertops. Step inside and be greeted by the allure of brand new vinyl plank floors throughout the home, adding a touch of contemporary elegance to the space. The cozy living room, freshly painted, features a charming fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings by the fire. 

The master bedroom, generously proportioned, offers an en-suite bath and a convenient walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your needs. 

As you venture outside, you'll discover a spacious backyard meticulously designed to prioritize your privacy, with thoughtful landscaping and a well-planned layout. Unwind on the expansive back deck, offering a serene retreat from the outside world. The front porch, adorned by magnificent Magnolia Trees, creates a tranquil oasis to relax and revel in the beauty of your surroundings. 

Rest assured, the refrigerator is included with the property, ensuring convenience and ease. 

Don't let this incredible opportunity slip away – call today to schedule an appointment and secure your place in this remarkable home at a great value.
